## 4. API Response Format

### Success
```json
{"success": true, "data": {...}, "message": "..."}
```

### Error
```json
{"success": false, "error": "CODE", "detail": "..."}
```

### Pagination
```json
{"success": true, "data": [...], "total": 100, "skip": 0, "limit": 10}
```

